OL,5, The former chairman of the Bank of     
OL,6, China has been arrested over suspicions
OL,7, of bribery and giving illegal loans.   
OL,9,FLiu Liange, chairman of the state-owned
OL,10,Fbank from 2019 to 2023, had resigned   
OL,11,Ffrom his position in March this year.  
OL,13,FWeeks later, authorities announced Mr  
OL,14,FLiu was facing corruption charges.     
OL,16,FThe 62-year-old is one of the most     
OL,17,Fsenior bankers to be ensnared in       
OL,18,FPresident Xi Jinping's anti-corruption 
OL,19,Fprobe into China's $60 trillion (#49   
OL,20,Ftrillion) financial sector.            
